<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 07:56:45 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>石雕狮头守望老街</title><link>https://some.pics/6a422539acca0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一个石雕狮头，鬃毛飘逸，从历史城区建筑的外立面上俯瞰街道。这是一件小巧的建筑艺术品，静静地经受住了时间的考验。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Stone lion carving with a majestic, flowing mane and a serious expression. The detailed texture conveys strength and timelessness." height="4360" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a422539acca0.jpg" width="3270"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 07:56:45 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a41fa2516e04</link><description>&lt;p&gt;夏末傍晚，埃尔福特路德纪念碑的剪影。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Man sieht die Silhouette eines Luther-Denkmals vor einem klassizistischen Backsteinhaus. " height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/soup/6a41fa2516e04.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://soup.some.pics"&gt;@soup&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 04:52:56 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a41aa2a8d7d4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;绵毛蓝卷&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Purple flowers on a green bush." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a41aa2a8d7d4.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 23:11:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>查帕拉尔锦葵</title><link>https://some.pics/6a41a5dc755e0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;灌丛锦葵&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A pink flower on a green bush." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://